SUMMARY:It Goes On
DTSTAMP:20260315T013642Z
DTSTART:20260326T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:$3 wine & poetry \\nReadings by Samar Abulhassan\\\, Kevin Emer
	son\\\, Ramon Isao\\\, and Arlene Naganawa \\nThursday\\\, March 26\\\, 7p
	m \\nDoors at 6pm \\nHugo House is delighted to partner with poet Jeanine 
	Walker and mixed media artist Aaron Counts to bring It Goes On to the Hugo
	 House stage! It Goes On features $3 glasses of wine\\\, $12 bottles\\\, a
	nd invaluable words. March 26 stars poets Samar Abulhassan and Arelene Nag
	anawa\\\, and fiction writers Kevin Emerson and Ramon Isao. Come on out to
